fel.cvut.af.model.input

Class SelectManyBasicOptionsInput

  • java.lang.Object
    • fel.cvut.af.model.input.Input
      • fel.cvut.af.model.input.BasicOptionsInput
        • fel.cvut.af.model.input.SelectManyBasicOptionsInput

  • @Entity
public class SelectManyBasicOptionsInput
extends BasicOptionsInput
    An entity class for Selectbox allowing multiple options to be selected.

    The options can represent different value types, see Option and his descendants.

    Use this class when Options hasn't too many elements. There is also an implementation of SelectMany where Options can be defined as a url leading to REST endpoint. See SelectManyEndpointOptionsInput.
